# OpenF1 Live Telemetry API Configuration
# OpenF1 has moved live telemetry to a paid tier. Past session data remains free.
# To view live F1 positioning during a race, you must register for an API key at https://openf1.org/

# 1. Rename this file from .env.example to .env
# 2. Paste your API key below
# 3. Restart your dev server (npm run dev) so Vite uncovers the new environment variable.

VITE_OPENF1_API_KEY=your_openf1_api_key_here
